{% set species = ptyasMajorRespImgs %}
{% set translation_link = species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated %}

{% extends "_layout_zh.njk" %} 
{% block hrefLanguage %}
         <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en-US" href="https://snakes-of-taiwan-test.netlify.app/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}.html" />
         <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://snakes-of-taiwan-test.netlify.app/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}.html" />
     <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh-TW" href="https://snakes-of-taiwan-test.netlify.app/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}_zh.html" />
     <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://snakes-of-taiwan-test.netlify.app/{{- species[0].nameLowerCaseHyphenated -}}_zh.html" />
{% endblock %}
{% block metaDescription %}
    ""
{% endblock %}
{% block headLinks %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/swiperJsGallery.min.css">       
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/infoPages.min.css">
{% endblock %}
{% block csp %}
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'none'; img-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com www.google-analytics.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; script-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js; media-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com www.google-analytics.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; style-src 'self' https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css; font-src 'self' data: application/font-woff">
{% endblock %}
{% block title %}
    {{ species[0].name }} - {{ species[0].chineseName }}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    
    <div class="header-box">
        <h1 class="header--species" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].name }}</h1>
        <h2 class="header--name" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].commonName }}</h2>
        <h2 class="header--name">{{ species[0].chineseName }}</h2>
        <h3 class="header--status">{{ species[0].statusChinese }}</h3>
        <h4 class="header--danger">{{ species[0].dangerChinese }}</h4>
    </div>                      

    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-modal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-nonModal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-thumbs_zh.njk" %}

    <div class="text-box-container">
        <div class="text-box--species-media">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關影片
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=34WRHukf2hY">虎頭山發現在樹梢休息的青蛇 </a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mSIyyTx7cM0">另一條也在虎頭山發現的青蛇</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3ok3Jd12O4">兩位作者於陽明山與青蛇的近距離接觸</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    鄉野調查
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.fieldherpforum.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=990">睡覺的青蛇</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.fieldherpforum.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=1423">兩隻青蛇</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.fieldherpforum.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=2025">森林青蛇</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-box-container text-box-container-info">
        <div class="text-box--species">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    家族
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頷蛇科，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colubrinae" lang="en-US">Colubrinae</a> 亞科            
                    <br>
                    <span lang="en-US">Colubridae, subfamily <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colubrinae">Colubrinae</a></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    最大體長
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    130 cm
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    台灣棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    台灣全島海拔 1000 m 以下。常見蛇種。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    世界棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
 	

                    中/南中國（海南，河南，甘肅，安徽，四川，福建，廣東，廣西，貴州，湖南，湖北，江西，江蘇，陝西，浙江），台灣，北越南，寮國。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    外觀描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    Medium-sized snake; total length up to 130 cm. There are 15 rows of smooth and glossy scales; some males may have two to five rows of keeled scales near posterior vertebral line. Head is narrow, oval to slightly triangular; body is slender; tail is long. Eye is medium to large; iris is light dull yellow to light tan, dappled by diffuse black pigment and pupil is round, jet black, surrounded by ring of light brown. Tongue is dull red with stem darkened by diffuse black pigment and fork tips dark gray to black. Upper head, body and tail is uniform green to dark green without designs while the supralabials and the first to third scale rows may be lighter in color. Ventral surface is light to yellow green, may be more yellow in anterior part of body. Anal scale is divided and the subcaudal scales are paired.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    生態描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text"> 	
                    青蛇為日形性喜好棲息在潮濕的森林區域與農業用地附近的溫和蛇類。牠以蚯蚓以及昆蟲的幼蟲為食的習性建立了牠半樹棲的生活型態。當夜晚來臨時，喜歡在灌木或是樹梢休息。母蛇於春季到夏初之間會產下 4-13 枚 長寬約 3 x 1.5 cm 的卵。初生幼體約長 26 cm。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    學名與俗名
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>Ptyas: </i></span> 是一個有關蛇毒噴入男人眼睛的希臘傳說。
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>major</i></span> 的意思是"大的";
                    </div>

                    青蛇、青竹絲、翠青蛇。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    附註
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    和善的青蛇常常被誤認為 赤尾青竹絲 (<span lang="en-US"><i>T. s. stejnegeri</i></span>) 然後遭到殺害。其實這兩種蛇很好區分，赤尾青頭部呈現三角形、有著紅色的眼睛另外兩旁體側還各有一條白線延伸到赤紅色的尾部。青蛇頭是橢圓形、黑眼睛、體側沒白線、尾巴是全綠的。另外青蛇的鱗片顏色也比較亮，赤尾青的鱗片顏色較霧。                 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關連結
                </div>
                <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                    <li lang="en-US"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="https://reptile-database.reptarium.cz/species?genus=Ptyas&species=major">Reptile Database</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="translator-name">翻譯:周信甫</div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Swiper JS -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Initialize Swiper -->
    <script   src="js/mySwiper.min.js"></script>

{% endblock %}